cs.CY, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.IR 

This paper focuses on customer relationship management (CRM) and machine learning models for predicting customer behavior. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CY (Computers and Society), which includes research on social and economic aspects of computing. The paper also involves machine learning models, which suggests it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses identifying potential silent sufferers, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
